sources.title: Asteroid Vs Earth | Full Movie | Action Adventure Disaster
sources.description:
Asteroid Vs Earth - When a shower of massive meteors threatens an extinction level event on Earth, the world's greatest minds devise a dangerous plan that will take the planet off its axis in order to avoid the impact.
2014.  Stars: Tia Carrere, Jason Brooks, Tim Russ
